*化學獎：[[饭岛澄男|饭岛澄男]]、[[本多健一|本多健一]][[File:Wikinews_tag_obituary.png|18px]]、[[藤嶋昭|藤嶋昭]]、[[橋本和仁|橋本和仁]]、[[諸熊奎治|諸熊奎治]]、[[鈴木章|鈴木章]][[File:Nobel_prize_medal.svg|18px]]、[https://web.archive.org/web/20080118020307/http://www.phys.titech.ac.jp/laboratory/takayanagi.html 高柳邦夫]、[[玉尾皓平|玉尾皓平]]、[http://kotobank.jp/word/%E5%8F%88%E8%B3%80%E6%9B%BB 又賀曻] {{Wayback|url=http://kotobank.jp/word/%E5%8F%88%E8%B3%80%E6%9B%BB |date=20130509234420 }}[[File:Wikinews_tag_obituary.png|18px]]、{{link-ja|伊藤公一|伊藤公一}}[[File:Wikinews_tag_obituary.png|18px]]、[[岩村秀|岩村秀]]。
